nodes.text: A Human male served as the leader of a Czerka Corporation strike team. In 3643 BBY, the strike team apprehended former Czerka employee Kamus Orden on Tatooine, inside a Republic Strategic Information Service safehouse in Anchorhead. Before they could kill Orden, who had been working with SIS operative Fauler, a Republic-allied individual arrived at the safehouse. In the ensuing skirmish the entire strike team, including the leader, was killed.
The strike team leader had brown hair and eyes, and a brown mustache.

The team leader wore the uniform worn by most Czerka employees during the Cold War, which was green with yellow stripes. He also wore a belt, and two blasters hung at his thighs. A piece of technology covered his right eye.
